    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance, featuring the legendary S65 V8 engine with an 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This collector-grade specimen boasts impeccable paint depth and a chassis free of subframe stress. The M-Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) function with factory-spec precision. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain remains robust. Retaining its original matte interior finishes and staggered ZCP competition wheels, this is a mechanically flawless, investment-grade driver\u2019s machine.",
