    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one, and it shows. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original, with perfectly tight tolerances and factory-fresh seals. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free of any creases or bolster wear, and it still carries that subtle new-car scent. All electronics, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate climate controls, function with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of every service record, documenting proactive maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with seamless fluidity, and the undercarriage is as clean as the roof. It sits on original alloy wheels\u2014completely free of curb rash\u2014wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Included are both original keys, all owner's manuals, and the original window sticker. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
