      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This car is an absolute gem! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it\u2014always garage-kept and hand-washed. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition, inside and out, and it honestly still drives like it just rolled off the lot. You really won't find one cleaner than this! I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
