      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, it features eight individual throttle bodies and a cross-flow cylinder head design, delivering a seamless 8,400 RPM redline. The longitudinal 6-speed manual gearbox offers tactile engagement, paired with the M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This specimen is in showroom condition, showing no signs of rod bearing wear or subframe fatigue. The factory Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and aluminum multi-link suspension remain tight, ensuring the precise turn-in and mechanical grip characteristic of a factory-fresh chassis. A true turn-key, collector-quality masterpiece.",
